description:
The X Factor Winner's Story 2015



A look at the life-changing journey of 2015's The X Factor winner, from their initial auditions and live show performances right through to the nail-biting final and beyond. How is the 2015 champion coping with life in the spotlight, and what awaits them in the coming months? Featuring interviews with this year's contestants and judges.


Original Air Date: 20-Dec-2015
